{"name": "opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-json", "metadata": {"name": "opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-json", "version": "1.29.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Framework :: OpenTelemetry", "Framework :: OpenTelemetry :: Exporters", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Typing :: Typed"], "home_page": null, "license": "Apache-2.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["opentelemetry-api", "opentelemetry-sdk", "requests"], "summary": "Zipkin Span JSON Exporter for OpenTelemetry", "upload_time": 1733936525}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  pypi: |-\n    ```{image} https://badge.fury.io/py/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-json.svg\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-json/\n    ```\n---\n\n# OpenTelemetry Zipkin JSON Exporter\n\n{{ pypi }}\n\nThis library allows export of tracing data to [Zipkin](https://zipkin.io/) using JSON\nfor serialization.\n\n## Installation\n\n```\npip install opentelemetry-exporter-zipkin-json\n```\n\n## References\n\n- [OpenTelemetry Zipkin Exporter](https://opentelemetry-python.readthedocs.io/en/latest/exporter/zipkin/zipkin.html)\n- [Zipkin](https://zipkin.io/)\n- [OpenTelemetry Project](https://opentelemetry.io/)\n"], "modules": [{"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.version", "documentation": ["Copyright The OpenTelemetry Authors", "Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the \"License\");", "you may not use this file except in compliance with the License.", "You may obtain a copy of the License at", "http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0", "Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software", "distributed under the License is distributed on an \"AS IS\" BASIS,", "WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.", "See the License for the specific language governing permissions and", "limitations under the License."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.version.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json", "documentation": ["# OpenTelemetry Zipkin JSON Exporter\n\nThis library allows to export tracing data to [Zipkin](https://zipkin.io/).\n\n# Usage\n\nThe **OpenTelemetry Zipkin JSON Exporter** allows exporting of [OpenTelemetry]\ntraces to [Zipkin]. This exporter sends traces to the configured Zipkin\ncollector endpoint using JSON over HTTP and supports multiple versions (v1, v2).\n\n```python\nimport requests\n\nfrom opentelemetry import trace\nfrom opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json import ZipkinExporter\nfrom opentelemetry.sdk.trace import TracerProvider\nfrom opentelemetry.sdk.trace.export import BatchSpanProcessor\n\ntrace.set_tracer_provider(TracerProvider())\ntracer = trace.get_tracer(__name__)\n\n# create a ZipkinExporter\nzipkin_exporter = ZipkinExporter(\n    # version=Protocol.V2\n    # optional:\n    # endpoint=\"http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans\",\n    # local_node_ipv4=\"192.168.0.1\",\n    # local_node_ipv6=\"2001:db8::c001\",\n    # local_node_port=31313,\n    # max_tag_value_length=256,\n    # timeout=5 (in seconds),\n    # session=requests.Session(),\n)\n\n# Create a BatchSpanProcessor and add the exporter to it\nspan_processor = BatchSpanProcessor(zipkin_exporter)\n\n# add to the tracer\ntrace.get_tracer_provider().add_span_processor(span_processor)\n\nwith tracer.start_as_current_span(\"foo\"):\n    print(\"Hello world!\")\n```\n\nThe exporter supports the following environment variable for configuration:\n\n- {envvar}`OTEL_EXPORTER_ZIPKIN_ENDPOINT`\n- {envvar}`OTEL_EXPORTER_ZIPKIN_TIMEOUT`\n\n# API\n\n[opentelemetry]: https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-python/\n[specification]: https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-specification/blob/main/specification/sdk-environment-variables.md#zipkin-exporter\n[zipkin]: https://zipkin.io/\n", "Copyright The OpenTelemetry Authors", "Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the \"License\");", "you may not use this file except in compliance with the License.", "You may obtain a copy of the License at", "http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0", "Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software", "distributed under the License is distributed on an \"AS IS\" BASIS,", "WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.", "See the License for the specific language governing permissions and", "limitations under the License."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.DEFAULT_ENDPOINT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.REQUESTS_SUCCESS_STATUS_CODES", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.ZipkinExporter", "bases": ["SpanExporter"], "methods": [{"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.ZipkinExporter.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": {"name": "Protocol", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.encoder.Protocol", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "endpoint", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "local_node_ipv4", "type": {"name": "IpInput", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.node_endpoint.IpInput", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "local_node_ipv6", "type": {"name": "IpInput", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.node_endpoint.IpInput", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "local_node_port", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "max_tag_value_length", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "timeout", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "session", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "requests.Session", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.Session", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Zipkin exporter.\n\nArgs:\n    version: The protocol version to be used.\n    endpoint: The endpoint of the Zipkin collector.\n    local_node_ipv4: Primary IPv4 address associated with this connection.\n    local_node_ipv6: Primary IPv6 address associated with this connection.\n    local_node_port: Depending on context, this could be a listen port or the\n        client-side of a socket.\n    max_tag_value_length: Max length string attribute values can have.\n    timeout: Maximum time the Zipkin exporter will wait for each batch export.\n        The default value is 10s.\n    session: Connection session to the Zipkin collector endpoint.\n\n    The tuple (local_node_ipv4, local_node_ipv6, local_node_port) is used to represent\n    the network context of a node in the service graph."]}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.ZipkinExporter.export", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "spans", "type": {"name": "Sequence", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Sequence", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Span", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.trace.Span", "project": "opentelemetry-api"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "SpanExportResult", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.sdk.trace.export.SpanExportResult", "project": "opentelemetry-sdk"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.ZipkinExporter.shutdown", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.ZipkinExporter.force_flush", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "timeout_millis", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": [{"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.environ", "xref": {"fqname": "os.environ", "project": null}}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.IpInput", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.node_endpoint.IpInput", "project": null}}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.JsonV1Encoder", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.v1.JsonV1Encoder", "project": null}}, {"name": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.JsonV2Encoder", "xref": {"fqname": "opentelemetry.exporter.zipkin.json.v2.JsonV2Encoder", "project": n